Package net.jqwik.api

Annotation Interface PropertyDefaults

@Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,TYPE}) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Inherited @API(status=MAINTAINED, since="1.4.0") public @interface PropertyDefaults
Annotate a container class with @PropertyDefaults if you want to set defaults of Property attributes of all contained property methods.
